KogMaw.name: Kog'Maw
KogMaw.title: the Mouth of the Abyss
KogMaw.lore: Belched forth from a rotting Void incursion deep in the wastelands of Icathia, Kog'Maw is an inquisitive yet putrid creature with a caustic, gaping mouth. This particular Void-spawn needs to gnaw and drool on anything within reach to truly understand it. Though not inherently evil, Kog'Maw's beguiling naiveté is dangerous, as it often precedes a feeding frenzy—not for sustenance, but to satisfy its unending curiosity.
KogMaw.blurb: Belched forth from a rotting Void incursion deep in the wastelands of Icathia, Kog'Maw is an inquisitive yet putrid creature with a caustic, gaping mouth. This particular Void-spawn needs to gnaw and drool on anything within reach to truly understand...
allytips: Kog'Maw can outrange most champions with his Bio-Arcane Barrage ability.
Use Void Ooze to set up a perfect Living Artillery.
Make the most out of your Icathian Surprise.
enemytips: Kog'Maw doesn't have a good escape ability, so he is especially prone to ganks.
Run away from Kog'Maw after he dies!!!!
The range on Living Artillery increases each rank.
Bio-Arcane Barrage allows Kog'Maw to kill Baron Nashor extremely early. It can be valuable to ward Nashor when Kog'Maw completes his Blade of the Ruined King.

spells.name: Caustic Spittle
spells.description: Kog'Maw launches a corrosive projectile which deals magic damage and corrodes the target's armor and magic resist for a short time. Kog'Maw also gains additional attack speed.
spells.tooltip:
Passive: Kog'Maw gains {{ e2*100 }}% bonus attack speed.

Active: Launches a corrosive projectile that deals {{ e1 }} (+{{ a1 }}) Magic Damage to the first enemy hit and shreds its Armor and Magic Resist by {{ e3 }}% for {{ e4 }} seconds.

spells.name: Bio-Arcane Barrage
spells.description: Kog'Maw's attacks gain range and deal a percent of the target's maximum health as magic damage.
spells.tooltip: For {{ e3 }} seconds, Kog'Maw's basic attacks gain {{ e1 }} range and deal {{ e2 }}% <scaleAP>(+{{ f1 }})%</scaleAP> of the target's maximum health as bonus magic damage.

spells.name: Void Ooze
spells.description: Kog'Maw launches a peculiar ooze which damages all enemies it passes through and leaves a trail which slows enemies who stand on it.
spells.tooltip: Deals {{ e1 }} <scaleAP>(+{{ a1 }})</scaleAP> Magic Damage to enemies hit and leaves a trail on the ground for {{ e3 }} seconds, slowing enemies in it by {{ e2 }}%.

spells.name: Living Artillery
spells.description: Kog'Maw fires an artillery shell at a great distance dealing magic damage (increased significantly on low health enemies) and revealing non-stealthed targets. Additionally, multiple Living Artilleries in a short period of time cause them to cost additional Mana.
spells.tooltip:
Fires an artillery shot, damaging enemies above 40% health for {{ basedamagecalc }} to {{ middamagecalc }} magic damage based on their missing health.

If enemies are below 40% health, they take {{ maxdamagecalc }} magic damage instead.

Each subsequent shot within {{ manacostduration }} seconds costs {{ basecost }} more Mana (max {{ manacostcap }}).

passive.name: Icathian Surprise
passive.description: 4 seconds after dying, Kogmaw explodes, dealing true damage to surrounding enemies.
passive.tooltip: Upon dying, Kog'Maw starts a chain reaction in his body which causes him to detonate after 4 seconds, dealing {{ passivedamage }} true damage to surrounding enemies.
